node.text:
Introducing the Carolina Herrera Summer 2021 Collection. 

Notes from Creative Director @WesGordon: “Fashion is healing for the soul. Its freeing and it can make you feel powerful. The women I design for seek beauty in all its forms and this collection is our gift to them. 
 
When I first started to think about this collection and sketch, it was very emotional. It was in between lockdown and the gradual reopening of our atelier. Every time I came in to the city, to the garment district, to our offices to work with the team, it felt like falling in love with fashion all over again. 
 
Fashion is a way to celebrate the beauty of special moments, and making ordinary moments extraordinary. And right now, I want each piece to be unmistakably Herrera.  Colors more saturated.  Volumes even more voluminous.  Tailoring at its most feminine. Sleeves more dramatic. Polka dots always. Embroideries more luminous. 
I wanted to create a collection that is a reflection of this moment in our lives, through the prism of optimism, color, and celebration of the women that have been part of the fabric of Carolina Herrera.
 
We believe in beauty.  We believe in dreams. We believe the antidote to darkness is light.  And we believe fashion is magical.”

This shoot took place in accordance with New York City production health and safety guidelines.

node.title: Carolina Herrera New York Summer 2021 Collection

node.title: THE CONVERSATION Episode 3: LIFE IS IN THE DETAILS

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and jewelry.

node.text: There’s no bad time for an Alegria (color n° 410) moment. Boasting lip conditioning ingredients and intense color pay-off, our matte formula is your one stop shop for bold head-turning style. And did we mention it’s also available as a refill?  Buy online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com. #HerreraBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 17, 2021. May be an image of cosmetics.

node.text: Boost your warm weather looks and get that tropical sunshine effect with a healthy dose of color and whimsy courtesy of our pineapple charm and sunny lipstick caps. Kind of like vitamins for your style. Buy online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com. #HerreraBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and footwear.

node.text: Have you fallen head over heels for our matte finish in Polka Red (color n° 412) yet? Discover all 36 shades of our iconic lipstick in three finishes and create your very own bespoke ready-to-wear piece of jewellery thanks to our range of printed caps, accessories and charms! Buy online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com. #HerreraBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and cosmetics.

node.text: She’s a Pink Mania (color n° 004), maniac, on the dance floor! Keep it footloose and fancy free this summer with our Mini Tints in 8  irresistible shades. Perfect for on-the-go polish, their balm-like texture provides buildable color that’ll keep going as long as the music does. Buy online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com. #HerreraBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 15, 2021. May be an image of fragrance and cosmetics.

node.text: Say hello to your new summer essential. Providing just a hint of a tint, our Mini Tint in Carolina (color n° 007) is all you need to go from “I just woke up”, to “I woke up like this” in one buttery glide. Buy online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com. #HerreraBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 15, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: You’ll want to think twice before you reveal the secret to your ‘no makeup’ makeup look... Soft and super hydrating, our Mini Tint in Carolina (color n° 007) is the ultimate in effortless polish. Buy online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com. #HerreraBeauty

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 14, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and high-heeled shoes.

node.text: With its elegant silhouette and supple leather exterior, the Doma Insignia Satchel is effortlessly chic. Shown here with our Pre-Fall 2021 collection.  #CHDomaInsignia #CHInsignia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Channel Jean Shrimpton with this chic Doma Insignia Satchel and double-faced wool suit from our Pre-Fall 2021 collection. #CHDomaInsignia #CHInsignia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and footwear.

node.text: Handcrafted in butter-soft leather, this #CHCharroInsignia hobo adds nonchalant elegance to this knitted zebra motif dress from our Pre-Fall 2021 collection. #CHInsignia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CAROLINA HERRERA on August 12, 2021 tagging @sitabellan, and @jorgelopez_as. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text: They’re more than just friends — they’re chosen family. Even when the bright lights and great heights of a city like New York overwhelm, 212 Heroes @jorgelopez_as and @sitabellan always have each other.  #212CarolinaHerrera #212ForeverYoung
